WEBVTT

00:00:59.566 --> 00:01:00.907
or threatening.

00:01:03.082 --> 00:01:05.312
It's a place of loyalty and trust.

00:01:06.335 --> 00:01:08.478
For that reason,

00:01:08.502 --> 00:01:12.401
it's one of the few places
where we can fearlessly be ourselves

00:01:12.425 --> 00:01:15.058
and just ... talk.

00:01:16.533 --> 00:01:19.534
The talk, the shop talk, the conversation,

00:01:19.558 --> 00:01:22.199
that is the essence
of the black barbershop.

00:01:23.178 --> 00:01:26.056
I can remember going to the barbershop
with my dad as a kid.

00:01:27.134 --> 00:01:30.562
We went to Mr. Mike's barbershop
every other Saturday.